    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/7a4ff1b74e7709910f41025ac501076b.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>前线幸存者》是一款具有roguelite元素的激烈的自上而下的射击游戏，让你置身于战场上为生存而战的士兵之靴。无数的敌人从四面八方向你袭来，你需要使用你所有的技能和策略来保持生命。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/09a84e5002628afece678fcdc970d8f3.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>随着你在游戏中的进展，你将有机会提升等级并选择升级，这些升级可以提高你的武器效率，以及赋予你一系列的特殊能力。无论你是想专注于技能和速度，还是想火力全开，都有很多选择来满足你的游戏风格。<br><br>有了身临其境的游戏，具有挑战性的敌人，以及一系列可供解锁的自定义功能，《前线幸存者》是任何自上而下的射击游戏爱好者的必玩之作。<br><br>你准备好加入战斗，成为前线的幸存者了吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.poster.avif?t=1764958921\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.webm?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275220/extras/1df995bac6dd1f244d3bae663a980a57.mp4?t=1764958921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 占领营地，摧毁目标，征服战场<br></li><li> 指挥盟友，帮助你击败敌人<br></li><li> 以各种方式升级你的角色<br></li><li> 多个角色可供选择，有各自的技能和玩法<br></li><li> 解锁新的武器来消灭你的敌人</li></ul>",
